    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You create three rays of fire and hurl them at targets within range. You can hurl them at one target or several.</p><p>Make a ranged spell attack for each ray. On a hit, the target takes [[/damage 2d6 type=fire]] damage.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p></p><div data-roll-name-ancestor=\"At Higher Levels\" class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"1\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">At Higher Levels.</span></span> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, you create one additional ray for each slot level above 2nd.</p></div></div>",
